        Changes the seat status of one seat
        Parameters:
        i_rowNumber - Integer : the number of the specific row where the seat is
        i_seatnumber - Integer : the number of the seat inside the row
        e_Status - CSeat.EStatus : the new/target satus of our seat
        rentUntil - CDateStorage : the time till the seat will be free again, for example for the next movie
        Returns:
        true if it was possible otherwise false, if the seat wasn't inside the room
